ALBUM glamrock-audio.js

TRACK Play Note FEATURING playNote
  TAKES number, number
  GIVES nothing

TRACK Play Chord FEATURING playChord
  TAKES string, number
  GIVES nothing

TRACK Set Volume FEATURING setVolume
  TAKES number
  GIVES nothing

TRACK Set Tempo FEATURING setTempo
  TAKES number
  GIVES nothing

TRACK Set Instrument FEATURING setInstrument
  TAKES string
  GIVES nothing

TRACK Rest FEATURING rest
  TAKES number
  GIVES nothing

TRACK Play Frequency FEATURING playFrequency
  TAKES number, number
  GIVES nothing
